name: White Flag (for the Oceans) III
description: Video & Audio by Artist & Environmental Activist Carmen Danae Azor @carmendanae. Part of an ongoing series of Clean NFT’s used as tools for climate action. The performance-art piece is a meditation on raising a white flag for the warming Oceans and all the species we've already lost to extinction due to anthropogenic causes. 100% of the sale & royalties will go towards Ocean Conservation & Climate Action projects in the Dominican Republic where the performance took place. 60seconds, 2880 × 2160.
